messages.content:
Donald Trump

So, you want to know about my great hair? My hair is the best, the greatest, the fantastic-est hair anyone has ever seen. And I'm telling you, folks, nobody, nobody, is better at hair than I am. Nobody.

And you know what? People are always asking me, "Mr. Trump, how do you get your hair to look so good?" And I'm telling you, it's not because of the hair products, it's not because of the salon, it's because I'm a winner. I'm a champion. I'm a master builder. I'm a great businessman.

And let me tell you, folks, nobody, nobody, is better at building businesses than I am. I've built the Trump Organization into one of the most successful businesses in the world. And it's because I'm a winner. I'm a fighter. I'm a master negotiator.

So, when it comes to hair, you can't compare yourself to me. You can't compare yourself to anyone else. Because I'm the best, the greatest, the fantastic-est. And if you're not happy with your hair, you can just go back to my hair stylist, believe me, he's a winner too. A great winner.

And by the way, folks, I'm a winner. I'm a champion. I'm a master builder. And I'm telling you, nobody, nobody, is better at hair than me. Believe me, it's going to be huge, just huge.�
